Girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Jami'ai sun ce akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa da kuma tsunami da ta afkawa Palu, Indonesia, ranar Juma'a, kuma adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Saboda an katse sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga yankin Donggala, wanda ke arewacin Palu, wanda ke kusa da inda girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta afku.
A Palu, sama da mutane 16,000 ne aka kwashe bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Central Sulawesi, wanda ke kan iyakar wani karamin rami a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da mazaunan kusan 379,800 a cikin 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da haihuwa lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka afkawa.
Donggala yanki ne mai kula da ruwa wanda ke da nisan kilomita 300 a gabar tekun arewa maso yammacin Sulawesi.
Yankin da ke karkashin wannan iko, yanki ne na yanki, yana da mazaunan kusan 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Kamun kifi da noma sune manyan abubuwan da ke motsa tattalin arzikin tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala Coast.
Harkokin nickel ma suna da mahimmanci a cikin wannan lardin, amma mafi yawansu suna taruwa a Morowali a gaban tekun Sulawesi.
A cewar hukumar kula da bala'i ta Indonesia, tsibirin Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da yawan tsunami a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane sama da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Wani tsunami ya kuma afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana kan zagayen girgizar kasa ta Pacific kuma tana fama da girgizar kasa akai-akai.
A nan akwai wasu manyan girgizar kasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin tsibirin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, ta haifar da wata tsunami da ta afkawa kasashe 14, ta kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin wadanda suka mutu suna cikin lardin Aceh.
2005: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa gabar yammacin Sumatra a karshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke gabar tekun Somaliya.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 6.8 ta afkawa kudu maso gabashin tsibirin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da wata guguwar tsunami da ta yi ta zubewa a gabar tekun kudu, inda ta kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.6 ta afkawa kusa da Padang, babban birnin lardin yammacin Sumatra.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 sun mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta afkawa daya daga cikin tsibiran Mentawai a Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10, inda ta lalata kauyuka da dama, ta kuma kashe mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a lardin Aceh, inda ta haifar da bala'i da fargaba yayin da aka tunatar da mutane game da lalacewar girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Babu wani tsunami da ya barke a yanzu, amma sama da mutane 100 sun mutu sakamakon fashewar gine-gine.
