Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya na neman hukuncin kisa na musamman ga wadanda ake zargi da hare-haren ta'addanci a New Zealand
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya na neman hukuncin kisa na musamman ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas, wanda shine hukuncin kisa na musamman da ba a taba yi ba a jihar don laifin tarayya tun 1953.
An zargi Saipov, mai shekaru 30, da amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari kan hanyar hawan keke a gefen West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya yi wa masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawan keke a kan hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da ingancin hukuncin kisa, alkali zai buƙaci ya nuna cewa Saipov ya kashe "da gangan" wadanda aka kashe takwas kuma ya yi mummunan rauni "da gangan", a cewar sanarwar da aka gabatar game da neman hukuncin kisa da aka shigar a Kudancin New York.
A cewar takardun kotu, hukuncin kisa ne a kan dukkansu.
Makonni bayan harin, alkalin kotun tarayya ya yanke wa Saipov hukuncin kisa kan tuhume-tuhume 22, wadanda suka hada da tuhume-tuhume guda takwas na kisan kai, laifin cinikin haram, da kuma wasu da aka yi amfani da su a gaban kotun tarayya a kan aikata laifukan da suka shafi aikata laifuka, da kuma zargin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Mai gabatar da kara ya ce harin ya bukaci "tsarin da ya dace da kuma taka tsantsan", yana mai bayyana yadda Saipov ya aiwatar da shi a matsayin "mai zalunci, mai zalunci da rashin mutunci".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni da lalacewa ga dangi da abokaiDiego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", in ji bayanin game da yanayin rashin tausayi.
Wadanda suka mutu biyar ne daga 'yan yawon bude ido daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da yankin kudancin New York ya fara aiwatar da hukuncin kisa.
An yanke wa Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa a kan mai sayar da miyagun kwayoyi, amma an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumba na 2009.
A kwanan nan, an zartar da hukuncin kisa a cikin shari'ar tarayya ta New York a 1953 ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata, kuma an kashe su bayan an yanke musu hukuncin daurin rai don yin balaguro ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenbergs duka biyu ta wurin kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cewar takardun kotu, Saipov, wanda asalinsa dan Uzbekistan ne, ya nuna rashin tarbiyya a cikin kwanaki da kuma bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗi game da abin da ya yi.
A cewar zargin, Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa an sa shi ya kai harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya kuma nemi a nuna tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin.
Ya amsa laifin da aka yi masa a kan tuhume-tuhume guda 22.
David Patton, mai ba da shawara kan harkokin jama'a na tarayya, wanda ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun yi matukar takaici da hukuncin da mai gabatar da kara ya yanke.
Patton ya ce: "Muna ganin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar amsa kan tuhumar da ke da hukuncin daurin rai a kurkuku ba tare da damar sakewa ba zai kara wa dukkan wadanda abin ya shafa zafi".
Lauyoyin kare Saipov sun riga sun nemi mai gabatar da kara da kada ya nemi hukuncin kisa.
