Muna son kafa dokokinmu a cikin kasarmu.
Bone ya yi watsi da cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun bayan zaben 2016: "Hankalin da ake da shi cewa mutanen Burtaniya sun canza tunaninsu kuma suna son ci gaba ba gaskiya bane".
'Yar jam'iyyar Conservative ta Brexit, Andrea Jenkyns, ta kasance cikin tafiya, tana gaya wa manema labarai cewa: "Ina kawai cewa: Firayim Minista ya saurari jama'a".
Chequers ba shi da kyau tare da jama'a, jam'iyyun adawa ba za su zabe shi ba, ba shi da kyau tare da jam'iyyunmu da masu fafutukarmu, hakika ya tafi hanya kuma ya sa mu fara jefa kuri'a.
'Ka sauke masu duba ka fara sauraro.'
