Elite League: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallaye biyu a raga a Dundee
Dundee Stars sun yi kokarin gyara rashin nasarar da suka yi a gasar Elite League a ranar Juma'a da Belfast Giants, inda suka ci Dundee 5-3 a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun ci gaba da yin nasara biyu ta hanyar samun nasara biyu ta farko ta hanyar buga Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun jagoranci masu masaukin kafin Dwyer ya kama Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya ci kwallo a raga don Dundee kafin Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ci biyu don nasarar su.
Wannan ne karo na uku da kungiyar Elite League ta yi rashin nasara a kakar wasa ta bana ga Adam Keefe, wanda ya biyo baya don doke Dundee da ci 2-1 a Belfast a ranar Juma'a da daddare.
Wannan shi ne karo na hudu da kungiyoyin biyu suka yi a kakar wasa, yayin da Giants suka ci wasanni uku a baya.
Dwyer ya ci kwallo a wasan farko a minti na 3:35 daga taimakon Kendall McFaull, tare da David Rutherford ya ba Beauvillier damar ci gaba da minti huɗu.
A lokacin buɗewa mai ban sha'awa, Sullivan ya dawo da masu masaukin a cikin 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya zama mai ba da izini ga Cownie a 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants sun jagoranci farkon farawar yayin da suka ci kwallaye na biyu a daren karshe na zagaye na 1.
Masu masaukin sun sake haɗuwa, kuma Bouchard ya sake sanya su a kan layi tare da ci gaba da zira kwallaye a minti na 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun haɗu don taimakawa Nielsen ya ba Dundee damar farko a wasan karshe a zagaye na biyu, kuma ya tabbatar da nasara ga tawagarsa a zagaye na biyar a wasan karshe.
Giants, wanda a yanzu ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu daga cikin biyar da suka gabata, a gidan Milton Keynes a wasansu na gaba a ranar Juma'a.
Mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama ya mutu don ceton daruruwan mutane a cikin jirgin da ya tsere daga girgizar kasa
An yabi mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a Indonesia a matsayin jarumi bayan ya mutu saboda taimakawa jirgin sama wanda ke dauke da daruruwan mutane ya sauka lafiya.
Fiye da mutane 800 sun mutu kuma mutane da yawa sun bace bayan wata babbar girgizar kasa da ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi ranar Juma'a ta hanyar wani tsunami.
Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta ci gaba da afkuwa a yankin, kuma mutane da yawa sun makale a cikin wani babban shinge a garin Palu.
Amma duk da cewa abokan aikinsa suna tserewa don rayukansu, Anthonius Gunawan Agung, mai shekaru 21, ya ki barin matsayinsa a cikin hasumiyar kula da filin jirgin sama na Mutiara Sis Al Jufri na Palu.
Ya kuma ci gaba da matakan da ya kamata don tabbatar da cewa jirgin Batik Air Flight 6321 ya tashi lafiya.
Sai ya yi tsalle daga hasumiyar kula da zirga-zirga lokacin da ya yi tunanin za ta rushe.
Ya mutu a asibiti.
Jaridar ABC ta Australia ta ruwaito cewa kakakin kamfanin jirgin saman Indonesiya Yohannes Sirait ya ce wannan matakin zai iya ceton daruruwan rayuka.
Mun shirya wani jirgin sama daga Balikpapan a Kalimantan don kai shi babban asibiti a wani birni.
Amma abin takaici, mun rasa shi da safiyar yau kafin rundunar ta isa Palu.
Ya kara da cewa, "Zuciyarmu ta yi zafi da jin wannan".
A halin yanzu, hukumomi na tsoron cewa adadin mutanen da suka mutu na iya kaiwa dubbai, yayin da hukumar kula da bala'i ta kasar ke cewa samun damar zuwa garuruwan Donggala, Sigi da Boutong na da iyaka.
Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, mai magana da yawun hukumar ya ce: "An yi imanin cewa adadin wadanda suka mutu yana ci gaba da ƙaruwa saboda yawancin gawawwakin suna ƙarƙashin ƙasa, yayin da mutane da yawa ba za a iya tuntuɓar su ba".
Ruwa mai tsawon mita shida ya lalata Palu, wanda za a yi jana'izar mutane da yawa a ranar Lahadi.
Jiragen sama na soja da na kasuwanci suna kawo agaji da kayayyaki.
Risa Kusuma, mai shekara 35, ta gaya wa Sky News cewa: "Kowane minti, motar agaji tana kawo gawawwaki da yawa.
Ruwa mai tsafta yana da ƙarancin.
An yi fashi a kananan kasuwanni a ko'ina".
Jan Gelfand, shugaban kungiyar 'yan gudun hijira ta kasa da kasa a Indonesia, ya shaida wa CNN cewa, 'yan gudun hijira na Indonesia suna neman taimakon wadanda abin ya shafa, amma ba mu san abin da za su samu a wurin ba.
Wannan bala'i ne, amma zai iya zama mafi muni.
Shugaban Indonesia Joko Widodo ya isa Palu a ranar Lahadi kuma ya gaya wa sojojin kasar cewa: "Ina rokon ku da ku yi aiki dare da rana don kammala dukkan ayyukan da suka shafi kwashe mutane".
"Shin kun kasance a cikin wani yanayi mai ban tsoro?" CNN ta ruwaito.
